<p>What could be better than making a Doormat that senses a footstep (using capacitive methods) and plays a random star wars song like the opening theme or the imperial march or a famous phrase from the movie like ‚ÄúMay the force be with you !‚Äù ?</p>

<p>Presenting the <strong>Star Wars Theme Interactive Doormat</strong>.</p>

